location.fullValue: Highwood Plan, Orchard Place - Freedom Series

data.description: Stunning from top to bottom. With new carpet and paint throughout, this one is a must see to really appreciate all of the features and updates. From the moment you walk in the front door, the meticulous care of this home shows. The main level  features a flex room and access to the oversized two car garage. Upstairs is a huge kitchen with center island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry, office nook and access to the large deck. Completing this level is the large dining area, living room and half bath. The third level features a large owners suite with a huge walk-in closet with a custom closet system and 3/4 bathroom, two additional bedrooms, a full bath and laundry closet. Located in the highly sought after 196 school district and close to all of the amenities that Apple Valley has to offer. Cobblestone Lake community amenities include a playground, walking paths, pool and more.  Hurry, you do not want to miss out on this one!
